(C)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= 0\\
(x^\mu)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= \mu x ^{\mu-1}\\
(\sin x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= \cos x\\
(\cos x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= -\sin x\\
(a^x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= a^x \; \ln a (a &amp;gt; 0, a \not= 1)\\
(e^x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= e^x\\
(\log _a x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= \frac{1}{x \ln a} \; (a &amp;gt; 0, a \not= 1)\\
(\ln x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= \frac{1}{x}
